item.title: Rhinefalls
item.description: Introduction The Rhinefalls one of the most popular places to visit in Switzerland. We visited Rhinefalls and blown away by the sheer power of the Rhine Falls, particularly during the summer, where the water flows at an impressive rate of 600,000 litres per second.
